    "en": {
      "title": "Gotabaya is not protected - Singapore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Singapore government says that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who is currently in Singapore, has not sought asylum or protection in Singapore.",
        "The Singapore government also claims that he has come to Singapore for a personal visit. The Saudi plane carrying Mr. Gotabaya Rajapaksa has reached Singapore at 7.17 pm Singapore time.",
        "\"He has not sought asylum and he will not be granted any protection. Singapore does not normally grant asylum claims,\" \u200b\u200bthe spokesman said.",
        "The plane of Saudi Airlines which took the President to Singapore is in Singapore.."
      ],
